  72:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****   /* This variable is updated in three ways:
  73:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****       1) by calling CMSIS function SystemCoreClockUpdate()
  74:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****       2) by calling HAL API function HAL_RCC_GetHCLKFreq()
  75:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****       3) each time HAL_RCC_ClockConfig() is called to configure the system clock frequency
  76:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****          Note: If you use this function to configure the system clock there is no need to
  77:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****                call the 2 first functions listed above, since SystemCoreClock variable is 
  78:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****                updated automatically.
  79:Src/system_stm32f0xx.c ****   */
